      "source_repo": "jina-ai/auto-gpt-web",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "**Set Your Goals, AI Achieves Them.** You can set up the initial role and goals for your AI buddy, without human's supervision, it will automatically leverage all of the resources it has to achieve your goal."
